            <td>SHA-256 hex digest of the CBDC batch manifest. Displayed in full (64 hex chars). A "⧉ Copy" button copies to clipboard. Operators can use this hash to cross-reference the batch in the Validation Desk or Audit &amp; Reports tab.</td>
          </tr>
